<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-52-0028 </DOCNO><TEXT>Optical gain characteristics of an Er/sup 3+/ -doped silica fiber havebeen studied by end pumping with a 1.48 {mu}m InGaAsP high-power laserdiode. A gain as high as 12.5 dB was obtained for an absorbed pump powerof 16 mW with a 3-m-long fiber. By constructing an Er/sup 3+/ fiber ringcavity with a 3 dB single-mode fiber coupler, we have obtained continuouswave laser oscillation at a wavelength of 1.553 {mu}m.</TEXT></DOC>